ventral; 65 Trilobate membrane, distal metatarsus of right leg II, dorsal." figureDoi-0="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6911181" figureDoi-1="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6911187" figureDoi-2="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6911189" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/6911181/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/6911187/files/figure.png" httpUri-2="https://zenodo.org/record/6911189/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Figs 47–65</figureCitation>
