<figureCitation box="[754,839,1261,1287]" captionStart="FIGURE 98" captionStartId="20.[151,250,1436,1460]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,956,1413]" captionTargetId="figure-372@20.[151,1436,956,1413]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="FIGURE 98. Distribution of the new genera and species in Malaysia, Brunei and Papua New Guinea." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6911205" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6911205/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Fig. 98</figureCitation>
: orange squares).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1437,649,1324]" box="[199,658,1297,1324]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,403,1297,1323]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Species included.</emphasis>
